===Etymology===
From ''[[Equisetum]]'' (the only living genus) + [[-phyta]]

===Proper noun===
'''Equisetophyta'''

#{{botany}}: A [[botanical name]] for a [[taxon]] within [[kingdom]] [[Plantae]] that includes the [[horsetail]]s and [[scouring rush]]es. The taxon is traditionally given the [[rank]] of a [[division]].

